### Setting Default Models in Configuration

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/help/faq.md

Illustrates how to configure default AI models and aliases within the OpenClaw configuration file. This allows for persistent default model settings and custom shortcuts.

```json5
{
  env: { MINIMAX_API_KEY: "sk-...", OPENAI_API_KEY: "sk-..." },
  agents: {
    defaults: {
      model: { primary: "minimax/MiniMax-M2.1" },
      models: {
        "minimax/MiniMax-M2.1": { alias: "minimax" },
        "openai/gpt-5.2": { alias: "gpt" }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

--------------------------------

### Configure Model Allowlist with Aliases

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/concepts/models.md

Example JSON5 configuration demonstrating how to set a primary model and define aliases for other models within the agent configuration. This controls which models are available for use.

```json5
{
  agent: {
    model: { primary: "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5" },
    models: {
      "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5": { alias: "Sonnet" },
      "anthropic/claude-opus-4-5": { alias: "Opus" }
    }
  }
}
```

--------------------------------

### Configure Agent Models and Aliases in JSON5

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/gateway/configuration.md

This snippet demonstrates how to define a model catalog with specific parameters and aliases for different AI models. It includes settings for temperature and maxTokens, and shows how to map provider-specific model IDs to user-friendly aliases.

```json5
{
  agents: {
    defaults: {
      models: {
        "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929": {
          params: { temperature: 0.6 }
        },
        "openai/gpt-5.2": {
          params: { maxTokens: 8192 }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

```json5
{
  agents: {
    defaults: {
      models: {
        "anthropic/claude-opus-4-5": { alias: "opus" },
        "minimax/MiniMax-M2.1": { alias: "minimax" }
      },
      model: {
        primary: "anthropic/claude-opus-4-5",
        fallbacks: ["minimax/MiniMax-M2.1"]
      }
    }
  }
}
```

```json5
{
  agents: {
    defaults: {
      models: {
        "anthropic/claude-opus-4-5": { alias: "Opus" },
        "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-1": { alias: "Sonnet" },
        "openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-r1:free": {},
        "zai/glm-4.7": {
          alias: "GLM",
          params: {
            thinking: {
              type: "enabled",
              clear_thinking: false
            }
          }
        }
      },
      model: {
        primary: "anthropic/claude-opus-4-5",
        fallbacks: [
          "openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-r1:free",
          "openrouter/meta-llama/llama-3.3-70b-instruct:free"
        ]
      },
      imageModel: {
        primary: "openrouter/qwen/qwen-2.5-vl-72b-instruct:free",
        fallbacks: [
          "openrouter/google/gemini-2.0-flash-vision:free"
        ]
      },
      thinkingDefault: "low",
      verboseDefault: "off",
      elevatedDefault: "on",
      timeoutSeconds: 600,
      mediaMaxMb: 5,
      heartbeat: {
        every: "30m",
        target: "last"
      },
      maxConcurrent: 3,
      subagents: {
        model: "minimax/MiniMax-M2.1",
        maxConcurrent: 1,
        archiveAfterMinutes: 60
      },
      exec: {
        backgroundMs: 10000,
        timeoutSec: 1800,
        cleanupMs: 1800000
      },
      contextTokens: 200000
    }
  }
}
```

