### Configuring Model Aliases

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/help/faq.md

Shows how to define custom aliases for AI models in the OpenClaw configuration. These aliases simplify model selection via slash commands.

```json5
{
  agents: {
    defaults: {
      model: { primary: "anthropic/claude-opus-4-5" },
      models: {
        "anthropic/claude-opus-4-5": { alias: "opus" },
        "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5": { alias: "sonnet" },
        "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5": { alias: "haiku" }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

--------------------------------

### Configure Agent Default Model

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/gateway/configuration.md

Specifies the primary AI model to be used by the agent, formatted as 'provider/model'. It also details how model aliases are resolved and provides an example for configuring Z.AI models, which require an API key.

```plaintext
agents.defaults.model.primary = "anthropic/claude-opus-4-5"
```

```plaintext
agents.defaults.models.Opus.alias = "anthropic/claude-opus-4-5"
```

```plaintext
agents.defaults.model.primary = "zai/glm-4.7"
```

--------------------------------

### OpenClaw Configuration for ZAI GLM Model

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/providers/glm.md

This JSON configuration snippet sets up environment variables and default agent models in OpenClaw. It specifies the ZAI API key for authentication and designates 'zai/glm-4.7' as the primary model for agents.

```json
{
  "env": { "ZAI_API_KEY": "sk-..." },
  "agents": { "defaults": { "model": { "primary": "zai/glm-4.7" } } }
}
```

--------------------------------

### Configuration Snippet for Z.AI GLM Models in OpenClaw

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/providers/zai.md

A JSON configuration snippet demonstrating how to set the ZAI_API_KEY environment variable and specify a default GLM model for OpenClaw agents.

```json
{
  env: { ZAI_API_KEY: "sk-..." },
  agents: { defaults: { model: { primary: "zai/glm-4.7" } } }
}
```

