### Configure Agent Model and Defaults

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/README.md

Sets the default AI model for the agent. This is a minimal configuration example for `openclaw.json`.

```json5
{
  agent: {
    model: "anthropic/claude-opus-4-5"
  }
}
```

--------------------------------

### Configure Default Agent Model (JSON)

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/platforms/raspberry-pi.md

Sets the default primary and fallback AI models for OpenClaw agents. This JSON configuration specifies 'anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-20250514' as the primary model and 'openai/gpt-4o-mini' as a fallback.

```json
{
  "agents": {
    "defaults": {
      "model": {
        "primary": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-20250514",
        "fallbacks": ["openai/gpt-4o-mini"]
      }
    }
  }
}
```

--------------------------------

### Configure Synthetic Anthropic-Compatible Endpoint

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/gateway/configuration.md

This configuration enables the use of Synthetic's models through an Anthropic-compatible API. It requires the SYNTHETIC_API_KEY and defines the model's endpoint, including its context window and maximum token limits.

```json5
{
  env: { SYNTHETIC_API_KEY: "sk-..." },
  agents: {
    defaults: {
      model: { primary: "synthetic/hf:MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-M2.1" },
      models: { "synthetic/hf:MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-M2.1": { alias: "MiniMax M2.1" } }
    }
  },
  models: {
    mode: "merge",
    providers: {
      synthetic: {
        baseUrl: "https://api.synthetic.new/anthropic",
        apiKey: "${SYNTHETIC_API_KEY}",
        api: "anthropic-messages",
        models: [
          {
            id: "hf:MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-M2.1",
            name: "MiniMax M2.1",
            reasoning: false,
            input: ["text"],
            cost: { input: 0, output: 0, cacheRead: 0, cacheWrite: 0 },
            contextWindow: 192000,
            maxTokens: 65536
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  }
}
```

